summary: This is a skykids Saria Racemenu Preset
descriptionHtml:
we all know the story of me trying to find characters for my LOZ play through so ill make it quick. i wanted Saria, looked 3 hours, found no Saria, made Saria. you can make this better and upload it but credit me for Farore's sake, you can turn her into a follower but credit me. BAM! ok now lets talk requirements.

Requirements

Skykids (be warned that it is on an adult modders site so you will most likly see boobs all you have to do is download and install it and all youll need is the race.) [url=http://www.loverslab.com/topic/22395-wip-skykids-child-races-other-technical-goodies-no-more-armor-patcher-new-cots-r2-race62215/]http://www.loverslab.com/topic/22395-wip-skykids-child-races-other-technical-goodies-no-more-armor-patcher-new-cots-r2-race62215/[/url]
